<head>WEIGHT</head>
    <list type="translations">
        <item xml:lang="zh">重量</item>
    </list>
<div type="definition">
<p>DEGREE of FORCE by which a THING is being NATURALLY PULLED TOWARDS the EARTH.</p>
    </div>
